</div></div><!--[--><div class="carousel__item" style="" data-v-46ba3a95><img src="/thumbs/products/l/1301601-canon-pixma-g6020.webp" width="500" height="500" loading="lazy" data-v-46ba3a95></div><div class="carousel__item" style="display:none;" data-v-46ba3a95><img src="/thumbs/brands/l/8-canon_logo.webp" width="500" height="500" loading="lazy" data-v-46ba3a95></div><!--]--></div><div class="clearfix" data-v-46ba3a95><div class="gallery__tile-container" data-v-46ba3a95><!--[--><div class="image gallery__tile" data-v-46ba3a95><div class="image" data-v-46ba3a95><img loading="lazy" src="/thumbs/products/l/1301601-canon-pixma-g6020.webp" alt="Canon PIXMA G6020 #1" data-v-46ba3a95></div><!----><!----></div><div class="image gallery__tile" data-v-46ba3a95><div class="image" data-v-46ba3a95><img loading="lazy" src="/thumbs/brands/l/8-canon_logo.webp" alt="Canon logo" data-v-46ba3a95></div><!----><!----></div><!--]--></div></div></div><div class="d-flex flex-grow-1 flex-column" data-v-54e0e672 data-v-02a1e486><h2 class="pb-2" data-v-02a1e486>Canon PIXMA G6020 specifications</h2><p data-v-02a1e486>You will find below the product specifications and the manual specifications for the Canon PIXMA G6020.</p><p style="white-space:pre-wrap;" data-v-02a1e486>The Canon PIXMA G6020 is a printer designed to meet the modern printing needs of homes and small offices. This printer serves as a reliable all-in-one solution with print, copy, scan, and fax capabilities. It boasts of high page yield, low running costs, and efficient printing technology. With its refillable MegaTank ink system, it can print up to 6,000 pages in black and 7,700 pages in colour without the need for constant ink replacement. Its automatic document feeder and duplex printing feature allow for fast and practical printing, scanning, and copy tasks. This printer supports various mobile printing options, including Canon PRINT app, AirPrint, Mopria Print Service, and Google Cloud Print. The Canon PIXMA G6020 produces crisp and vivid prints with a maximum resolution of 4800 x 1200 dpi. It also has a user-friendly interface and can connect wirelessly via Wi-Fi or Ethernet. The compact and stylish design makes it a great addition to any home office or workspace. Its advanced features, functionality, and affordability make it a reliable investment for those who need a printer that delivers great print quality and cost-effective printing.</p><div class="feature-logos pb-4" data-v-02a1e486><!--[--><!--]--></div><div id="specs" class="" data-v-02a1e486><div data-v-02a1e486><div class="specs__highlight" data-v-02a1e486><!--[--><!--]--></div><div class="card mb-4" data-v-02a1e486><h5 class="d-flex" data-v-02a1e486><div class="app-icon size-null task-list-approve me-2" data-v-02a1e486><svg enable-background="new 0 0 24 24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="m11.25 15.011c-.414 0-.75-.336-.75-.75s.336-.75.75-.75h5.25c.414 0 .75.336.75.75s-.336.75-.75.75z"/><path d="m11.25 19.511c-.414 0-.75-.336-.75-.75s.336-.75.75-.75h5.25c.414 0 .75.336.75.75s-.336.75-.75.75z"/><circle cx="8.25" cy="14.261" r="1.125"/><path d="m11.25 10.511c-.414 0-.75-.336-.75-.75s.336-.75.75-.75h5.25c.414 0 .75.336.75.75s-.336.75-.75.75z"/><circle cx="8.25" cy="9.761" r="1.125"/><circle cx="8.25" cy="18.761" r="1.125"/><path d="m4.5 24.011c-1.241 0-2.25-1.009-2.25-2.25v-15.75c0-1.241 1.009-2.25 2.25-2.25h3.063c.361-2.128 2.247-3.75 4.437-3.75s4.076 1.621 4.437 3.75h3.063c1.241 0 2.25 1.009 2.25 2.25v15.75c0 1.241-1.009 2.25-2.25 2.25zm0-18.75c-.414 0-.75.336-.75.75v15.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75h15c.414 0 .75-.336.75-.75v-15.75c0-.414-.336-.75-.75-.75h-3.75c-.414 0-.75-.336-.75-.75 0-1.654-1.346-3-3-3s-3 1.346-3 3c0 .414-.336.75-.75.75z"/><circle cx="12" cy="4.136" r="1.125"/></svg></div> General</h5><table class="table table-sm" data-v-02a1e486><tbody data-v-02a1e486><tr data-v-02a1e486><td class="text-muted" data-v-02a1e486>Brand</td><td itemprop="brand" data-v-02a1e486><a href="/canon" class="" data-v-02a1e486>Canon</a></td></tr><tr data-v-02a1e486><td class="text-muted" data-v-02a1e486>Model</td><td itemprop="name" data-v-02a1e486>PIXMA G6020</td></tr><tr data-v-02a1e486><td class="text-muted" data-v-02a1e486>Product</td><td itemprop="category" data-v-02a1e486><a href="/computers-and-accessories/printers" class="" data-v-02a1e486>printer</a></td></tr><!----><tr data-v-02a1e486><td class="text-muted" data-v-02a1e486>Language</td><td data-v-02a1e486>English</td></tr><tr data-v-02a1e486><td class="text-muted" data-v-02a1e486>Filetype</td><td data-v-02a1e486>User manual (PDF)</td></tr></tbody></table></div><!--[--><!--]--></div></div><!----></div><div data-v-54e0e672 data-v-ef4a26a9><!----></div><div class="ad-placeholder my-3" style="" data-v-54e0e672 data-v-65ff48d5><!----><!----></div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/FAQPage" class="faq-listing" data-v-54e0e672 data-v-54cc08af><h3 class="pb-2 h1" data-v-54cc08af>Frequently Asked Questions</h3><p data-v-54cc08af>Can&#39;t find the answer to your question in the manual? You may find the details you need in the FAQs about the Canon PIXMA G6020 listed below.</p><div class="ad-placeholder my-3" style="" data-v-54cc08af data-v-65ff48d5><!----><!----></div><div class="faq-item" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question" data-v-54cc08af data-v-d2242a65><h4 class="h5" itemprop="text name" data-v-d2242a65><!--[-->How to Print from the Lower Paper Tray on Canon PIXMA G6020 - Easy Printing Guide<!--]--></h4><div itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer" data-v-d2242a65><div itemprop="text" data-v-d2242a65><!--[--><div class="video-wrapper mb-2" data-v-54cc08af><iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/mv5MFPKLNYw" width="100%" height="100%" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" data-v-54cc08af></iframe></div><!--]--></div><!----></div></div><!--[--><!--[--><div class="faq-item" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question" data-v-54cc08af data-v-d2242a65><h4 class="h5" itemprop="text name" data-v-d2242a65><!--[-->Why is my Canon PIXMA G6020 not printing?<!--]--></h4><div itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer" data-v-d2242a65><div itemprop="text" data-v-d2242a65><!--[-->Ensure that the printer is connected to a power source and turned on. Check if the printer&#39;s ink tanks are properly filled and securely installed. Additionally, verify that the printer is connected to the computer or network properly.<!--]--></div><div class="faq-item__footer" data-v-d2242a65><button class="outline-primary like sm" data-v-d2242a65><div class="app-icon size-null thumbs-up" data-v-d2242a65><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8.759 1.104 C 8.344 1.205,7.888 1.528,7.668 1.878 C 7.533 2.093,7.470 2.268,7.373 2.701 C 7.237 3.308,7.137 3.564,6.885 3.950 C 6.714 4.212,6.483 4.456,6.105 4.775 C 5.773 5.055,5.605 5.229,5.426 5.480 C 5.310 5.642,5.067 6.100,5.067 6.156 C 5.067 6.228,5.022 6.175,4.949 6.020 C 4.791 5.679,4.385 5.362,4.005 5.283 C 3.814 5.243,1.946 5.243,1.755 5.283 C 1.306 5.376,0.911 5.729,0.743 6.187 L 0.680 6.360 0.680 9.573 L 0.680 12.787 0.740 12.945 C 0.904 13.376,1.273 13.716,1.694 13.826 C 1.925 13.886,3.835 13.886,4.066 13.826 C 4.488 13.716,4.861 13.371,5.020 12.943 C 5.073 12.801,5.080 12.721,5.093 12.067 L 5.107 11.347 5.194 11.514 C 5.392 11.893,5.666 12.243,5.934 12.462 C 6.195 12.674,7.344 13.434,7.594 13.560 C 7.859 13.693,8.192 13.796,8.492 13.838 C 8.618 13.856,9.272 13.866,10.195 13.866 C 11.857 13.866,11.906 13.862,12.248 13.696 C 12.481 13.584,12.748 13.367,12.897 13.170 C 13.102 12.898,13.199 12.656,13.272 12.237 C 13.290 12.132,13.314 12.098,13.440 11.996 C 13.889 11.632,14.129 11.091,14.101 10.509 L 14.089 10.251 14.221 10.160 C 14.495 9.971,14.753 9.605,14.870 9.241 C 14.923 9.073,14.939 8.968,14.941 8.760 C 14.943 8.461,14.910 8.289,14.794 8.007 L 14.715 7.813 14.